	* shell/rb-shell-player.c: (rb_shell_player_sync_with_source):
	Don't actually disable the seek bar for non-seekable songs,
	because we can't reliably tell yet.

2006-08-19  Jonathan Matthew  <jonathan@kaolin.wh9.net>

