2006-04-17  James Livingston  <doclivingston@gmail.com>

	Updated documentation from Baptiste Mille-Mathias <bmm80@free.fr>
	and "vic".

	* help/C/figures/rb-iradio-main.png:
	* help/C/figures/rb-notification-area-menu.png:
