	* shell/rb-shell-player.c: (rb_shell_player_set_property),
	(rb_shell_player_sync_buttons),
	(rb_shell_player_selection_changed_cb): watch for the
	"selection-changed" signal, so that the Song Properties get enabled.
	Closes bug 323694.

