	* configure.ac: Updated to require avahi >= 0.5.  Small fixes.

	* daapsharing/rb-daap-dialog.c:
	(rb_daap_password_dialog_new_run), (rb_daap_collision_dialog_new_run):
	HIG compliancy & images.

