2005-09-01  Colin Walters  <walters@verbum.org>

	* widgets/eggtrayicon.h: Prototype egg_tray_icon_have_manager.

	* widgets/eggtrayicon.c (egg_tray_icon_have_manager): Steal
	from gtkstatusicion.c.

